            <title>[JCR-2091] Searchability settings in PropertyDefinition</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-2091</link>
                <project id="10591" key="JCR">Jackrabbit Content Repository</project>
                        <description>Related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/JCR-1591&quot; title=&quot;JSR 283: NodeType Management&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JCR-1591&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the new JCR 2.0 property definitions contain settings for searchability of properties.&lt;br/&gt;
