currently the settings have no effect on what&amp;#39;s indexed/what&amp;#39;s searchable.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
i am not sure whether/how we want to implement the semantics of&lt;br/&gt;
the &amp;#39;searchable&amp;#39; node type attributes.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
wdyt, marcel?</comment>
                    <comment id="12718423" author="mreutegg" created="Thu, 11 Jun 2009 13:28:00 +0100"  >I think for the 2.0 release we should just leave things as they are. Later we can still use those settings instead of the current indexing configuration.</comment>
